{"tid":751892,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Viu]99台11:30 planB","createTime":"2018-07-22T09:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T12:09:33.000Z","uid":196216,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0ffc6934b6635c4336c7bb7ef10dd9ad2c4aec","tid":751892,"uid":196216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"真心問香港d黑社會劇仲有冇得做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇咗幾集viutv planB覺得都膠得黎有啲味道？<br />\n<br />\nViuTV劇集《PLAN B》喺噚晚首播，唔少網民都留言話好期待呢套劇，因為劇集只係播映半個鐘，所以故事情節嘅發展，當然係有待追看，喺第一集，故事係先由王宗堯、駱振偉（Thor）同陳炳銓（Danny）三個人展開，佢哋諗住綁架有錢女吳嘉熙(Cheronna)，結果觸發咗一段江湖風暴，身為話事人嘅田雞，搵咗陳啟泰出嚟平息。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180717/58452559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452559&d=jM4Xazfkj6lOjvklLJQOxdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=dbd6fa2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58452559&h=18d7bb59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180717/58452559</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172553_6df5d58133ebd491edfdc821c6876645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172553_6df5d58133ebd491edfdc821c6876645.jpg&h=ed7f8356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/164720_a8c266cede05d861da25113a93f9a6ee.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F164720_a8c266cede05d861da25113a93f9a6ee.JPG&h=16daadbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/170440_bc3aafc8710ec4ef2e42d3e95eb32093.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F170440_bc3aafc8710ec4ef2e42d3e95eb32093.jpg&h=b617f4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/164741_ddab9e463bb3e2279290f0c570195c00.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F164741_ddab9e463bb3e2279290f0c570195c00.JPG&h=9541fa8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52ad4b6d9158f45bb15c90c65d464f3bb37c01e8","tid":751892,"uid":196197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"堅持咗5集，真係頂唔順，放棄咗。<br />\n<br />\n係有誠意嘅，但係係咁不斷重複片段，大佬呀，你一集唔計廣告得嗰21分鐘，扣埋人物介紹得19分鐘多D，但係重複片段可能佔3分鐘咁滯..... 即係每集得16分鐘。陸駿光D戲係好好，但係泥鯭演技幼嫩，田雞講嘢個 tone 好撚唔自然，扣哂分。<br />\n<br />\n利申：無睇CCTVB 3年，平時只睇 ViuTV"},{"pid":"b13f1452c9acb41bf5f2be1200e3f9066686d0c9","tid":751892,"uid":196216,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心想support港劇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/200746_a1c24250e7be1d784528e00f989e724e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F200746_a1c24250e7be1d784528e00f989e724e.JPG&h=03816cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/200753_fe0b1f8b3f4872c29dd395925000d799.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F200753_fe0b1f8b3f4872c29dd395925000d799.JPG&h=57330d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/200801_7593a1fc98b04f5d2d4798e8915d35b3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F200801_7593a1fc98b04f5d2d4798e8915d35b3.JPG&h=f53f79c2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}